    public interface Deployment
extends Indexable, Refreshable<Deployment>, Updatable<Deployment.Update>, HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.management.resources.implementation.DeploymentExtendedInner>, HasManager<com.microsoft.azure.management.resources.implementation.ResourceManager>, HasName
